title: GoPro: Melissa Colborne Shreds in South Africa
description:
Top South African Female Wakeboarder, Melissa Colborne, spends a day at the cable park practicing her tricks. Following in the footsteps of her older brother Jason, she started wakeboaring in April 2009 and has shot to the top to become a national competitor.

Special Thanks to Chris Rogers.

Shot 100% on the HERO3+® camera 

Music
Two Eights "Gemma"
